Jemima West https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jemima_West 0 Jemima West (born 11 August 1987) is an Anglo-French actress. She is bilingual, growing up for most of her life in Paris, France. She is best known for playing Isabelle Lightwood in the film adaptation of The Mortal Instruments: City of Bones and Alice Whelan in the British drama series Indian Summers. She also appeared in the second season of The Borgias as Vittoria. Jemima_West ( born 11_August_1987 ) is an_Anglo-French_actress .
